underlying_goal: Assess the current implementation state of the GPQA prompt selection pipeline against its specification.
primary_success: Quickly and accurately assessed the status of a complex feature, identifying which parts were complete and which were missing, and providing a clear, actionable summary and path forward.
brief_summary: The user asked about the implementation status of the prompt selection pipeline. The assistant analyzed the codebase and determined that while the foundational modules were complete and tested, the main orchestration layer (`runner.py`) was missing, preventing end-to-end execution. It provided a detailed breakdown of completed vs. missing components and a clear plan for finishing the implementation.
